{"tid":1494720,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想問有冇咩牙醫好介紹","createTime":"2019-08-21T18:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T18:40:34.000Z","uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"726fc4252c8cd702e3eeefccffb36eb91b570d7f","tid":1494720,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:08:52.000Z","msg":"上個月月中開始37個隻牙有啲啲痛<br />\n開頭都以為似敏感牙齒<br />\n飲凍嘢勁撚酸痛<br />\n<br />\n我就冇乜點理到<br />\n但呢排痛到下顎同左腦神經都開始俾釘吉咁<br />\n我知睇牙好貴<br />\n呢兩個月又大洗咗<br />\n<br />\n可以有咩辦法處理好<br />\n一嚟就幾千蚊真係肉痛死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1373a588120aa3c2defa45a43bd5c9e2c79bd05b","tid":1494720,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:21:40.000Z","msg":"牙痛慘過大病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明白你既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n西灣河有間好好，太安樓對面，杜大牙牙根，未計牙套，4000up。<br />\n元朗有間係無比較既情況下都ok，齒盈坊，杜大牙牙根3000左右。<br />\nmk有間，cls，我睇睇下牙，無啦啦個醫生話我天生少左隻牙，當堂嚇一嚇，點知個醫生轉個頭話自己數錯數，仆街，1-40都數得錯。<br />\n<br />\n利申，已經杜左4隻牙根。"},{"pid":"8fe7ec8cf9ffc84e5cbda7c3f7a018dda85078e1","tid":1494720,"uid":59569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1373a588120aa3c2defa45a43bd5c9e2c79bd05b","tid":1494720,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:21:40.000Z","msg":"牙痛慘過大病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明白你既感覺。<br />\n<br />\n西灣河有間好好，太安樓對面，杜大牙牙根，未計牙套，4000up。<br />\n元朗有間係無比較既情況下都ok，齒盈坊，杜大牙牙根3000左右。<br />\nmk有間，cls，我睇睇下牙，無啦啦個醫生話我天生少左隻牙，當堂嚇一嚇，點知個醫生轉個頭話自己數錯數，仆街，1-40都數得錯。<br />\n<br />\n利申，已經杜左4隻牙根。"},"citedBy":1,"repl