" /><br />\n你都係問返個可信性高既牙醫會好d，因為好多牙醫係咪都叫你杜牙根。<br />\n我有fd本身有個牙醫叫佢杜牙根，佢唔信，去左第二間睇，另一個牙醫叫佢深層清潔牙肉果d，我都唔記得啦，總之就好返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:39:46.000Z","msg":"葵青<br />\n收晒皮係唔係唔會再復發先<br />\n做咩你要成日睇牙醫嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 我都覺好多醫生為賺錢而冇操守<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:07:46.000Z","msg":"齒盈坊，我係佢地到杜過牙同剝過牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地荃灣都有診所，我睇開許兆東，你可以去下，我覺得係幾好。<br />\n<br />\n手勢好真係無再痛過，起碼我4隻杜過牙根既牙都無事。<br />\n<br />\n我一年級果陣學童牙科保健睇左廿次，俾左廿蚊真係好抵睇。<br />\n醫生話我天生口腔分泌物比一般人多，好容易蛀牙乜乜乜，細個仲要每日填簿仔mark低食過d乜，俾個牙醫睇返，每隔幾日打黎問我老豆我d牙點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實細個無乜點食過垃圾食物，純粹唔鐘意用牙膏刷牙，我老母又由我用清水求其刷下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後個牙醫因爲我棚牙，first hon畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我本身訓覺成日磨牙或者用力咬實d牙，搞到起身牙較都痛埋，依家有帶牙套訓，總之就係煩<br />\n<br />\nbtw，如果你一隻牙唔搞，係會傳染俾第二隻牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=